  "text": "A set of ten dummy variables was representing the main effect within each of the five EQ-5D dimensions (Model 1) [CITATION_1] . The dummy variables for level 2 represents the main effect of movement from level 1 (no problems) to level 2 (moderate problems), and the dummy variables for level 3 represents the main effect of movement from level 1 (no problems) to level 3 (severe problems) ( Table 1 ).",
